messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.

I don't have the capability to access GPS or map apps directly. However, if you can find your latitude and longitude using a GPS device or a map application on your smartphone or computer and provide those coordinates here, I will be able to help determine your city.
